## ADDITIONS
* Added soyuz rocket and its platform
* Added large launch pad
* Added the blue rinse nuke
* Added assembly machine
* Added some building blocks
* Added volcanoes
* Added barbed wires
* Added spikes
* Added bobbleheads

## CHANGES
* Nuclear explosions will now use "Threaded DDA raytracer"
  * This means explosions will destroy blocks much faster
  * Can be changed in the config to older algorithm from 1.7.10
* Fire, balefire, phosphorus and blackfire player properties now will affect player

## FIXES
* Explosion algorithm now try to clear water at chunk borders
  * This works only for NEW algorithm
* Fixed server side loading client classes
* Fixed nuke mushroom cloud not rendering after explosion in sable sublevel
* Fixed obj model renderer breaking with veil installed
* Fixed obj model loader crashing the game
* Fixed vanilla armor not reducing damage